<h1>Welcome to your new app.</h1>
<p>
    This application is built as part of a .NET MAUI assessment. It demonstrates API integration, data binding,
    and navigation in a multi-platform application.
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Fetches product list from <code>https://fakestoreapi.com/products</code></li>
    <li>Displays detailed product information on selection</li>
    <li>Uses <strong>HttpClient</strong> for all API calls</li>
    <li>No hardcoded data — everything is dynamically loaded</li>
</ul>

<p>
    Use the navigation menu to explore the product list.
</p>
